ActNorthwest Territories Act
SubjectLand Exchange Agreement between the Government of the Northwest Territories and the Government of Canada
PrecisOrder (1) consenting to the relinquishment of the administration and control from the Commissioner of Northwest Territories, in perpetuity, of the public lands described in the Schedule I; and (2) transferring to the Commissioner of the Northwest Territories, in perpetuity, the administration and control of the public lands described in the Schedule II.
